sellerCard.oneLiner: Professional Graphic Designer, Developer and Certified UX UI Designer
sellerCard.description: Welcome to Dee7 Studio on Fiverr! We specialize in crafting stunning websites and dynamic digital content. Our team excels in Web Design, Marketing Design, and Infographic Creation, offering customized solutions that captivate and engage. Partner with us for innovative designs tailored to your brand's needs. Let's elevate your online presence together!

description.content:
Looking for a Professional Responsive Website for Your Business? Choose Dee7Studio!


Please contact us before placing an order :)


About Us


At Dee7Studio, we bring over 10 years of experience in content marketing, branding, and web design to help businesses like yours stand out. From infographics and blog management to strategic branding and user-centric web design, we focus on delivering exceptional results tailored to your audience.


Websites are designed to showcase your brand and attract as much of your targeted visitors as possible and point them in the right direction.


What You Will Receive:

  • Competitive Research
  • UX and UI Design in Figma
  • Prototyping in Figma
  • Development in Webflow or Wordpress
  • Full Ownership: You own the artwork.
  • Data Safety: Your information is secure.
  • Creative Designs: To highlight your content.
  • Satisfaction Guaranteed: Or your money back!


NOTE: The basic and standard packages don't include branding. 


Check out other awesome gigs on my profile here: 

www.fiverr.com/dreejc7

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
* Brief/specification including your business, audience, competitors, examples of designs that you like most
* Branding materials if there are any

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you create Prototypes, so I can see the design in action?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I do provide prototypes in Figma

questionsAndAnswers.question: I would like to order a different quantity of pages. What can we do?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Just send me a number of pages with a short description of your desired outcome, so I can send you a custom quotation.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is a Fiverr PRO seller?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Hand-vetted sellers by Fiverr's customer success team ensuring a high-end service with top-quality deliverables.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is your process like?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I use the Agile collaborative process with draft sprints, usually, a few draft iterations are required to ensure the best results and achievement of your business goals

reviews.comment: Brilliant as always. - highly recommended for any website projects

Working with this team to help me rebrand my Compnay was a great experience.  They helped implement what I had in mind, and frame it in a way to make the site better,  Now onto he next steps of the  relaunch.

Andrej was great to work with; he maintained professionalism and a good attitude throughout the project, and all requested changes were completed. I would recommend Andrej's services to the broad Fiverr community. 

My website looks fantastic, and all the new features work like charms. Thank you, Andrej, and I hope we can work again.
